  "question": "Toula went to the bakery and bought various types of pastries. She bought 3 dozen donuts which cost $68 per dozen, 2 dozen mini cupcakes which cost $80 per dozen, and 6 dozen mini cheesecakes for $55 per dozen. How much was the total cost?",
  "prompt": "Toula went to the bakery and bought various types of pastries. She bought 3 dozen donuts which cost $68 per dozen, 2 dozen mini cupcakes which cost $80 per dozen, and 6 dozen mini cheesecakes for $55 per dozen. How much was the total cost?\n\nShow your work briefly and put the final answer in \\boxed{}.",
  "gold_answer": "694",
  "generated_text": "To find the total cost, we need to calculate the cost for each type of pastry and then sum them up.\n\n**Step 1: Calculate the cost of the donuts.**\nToula bought 3 dozen donuts at $\\$68$ per dozen.\n$$ \\text{Cost}_{\\text{donuts}} = 3 \\times 68 $$\n$$ 3 \\times 60 = 180 $$\n$$ 3 \\times 8 = 24 $$\n$$ 180 + 24 = 204 $$\nSo, the cost of the donuts is $\\$204$.\n\n**Step 2: Calculate the cost of the mini cupcakes.**\nToula bought 2 dozen mini cupcakes at $\\$80$ per dozen.\n$$ \\text{Cost}_{\\text{cupcakes}} = 2 \\times 80 $$\n$$ 2 \\times 80 = 160 $$\nSo, the cost of the cupcakes is $\\$160$.\n\n**Step 3: Calculate the cost of the mini cheesecakes.**\nToula bought 6 dozen mini cheesecakes at $\\$55$ per dozen.\n$$ \\text{Cost}_{\\text{cheesecakes}} = 6 \\times 55 $$\n$$ 6 \\times 50 = 300 $$\n$$ 6 \\times 5 = 30 $$\n$$ 300 + 30 = 330 $$\nSo, the cost of the cheesecakes is $\\$330$.\n\n**Step 4: Calculate the total cost.**\nAdd the costs from all three types of pastries together.\n$$ \\text{Total Cost} = \\text{Cost}_{\\text{donuts}} + \\text{Cost}_{\\text{cupcakes}} + \\text{Cost}_{\\text{cheesecakes}} $$\n$$ \\text{Total Cost} = 204 + 160 + 330 $$\n$$ 204 + 160 = 364 $$\n$$ 364 + 330 = 694 $$\n\nThe total cost is $\\$694$.\n\n\\boxed{694}\n",
